* Rage shook her head and spat onto the ground, while in a rush to kill her 
prey she hadn't noticed how awful it's blood tasted!
She shook her head again and turned towards the forest, she would never 
attack another raptor as long as it's blood tasted like that!!
Rage slowly entered into the thick brush and moved on towards an area that 
she knew water dwelled, she had to get the taste out of her mouth...NOW!
She snarled as she moved on and disappeared into the shadows of the 
forest...so much for supper!*
